t:
I had reported that my daughter was missing.

Today the police called, she had been found, well and alive.




When I went to where I had buried her, I couldn't find her body.
c:
She's ready to return home.



Three years ago, on this day, we were readying for YourQuote launch. Tomorrow YourQuote completes its 3rd anniversary. Talk about what were you doing #threeyearsago #collab #YourQuoteAndMine
